  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York City High Line, 2007 is a polyline theme that represents an abandoned elevated freight rail line in New York City known as the \"High Line\". Raw data was acquired from files from the New York State Department of Transportation. Data is provided in the projection NAD83 to align with the NYCMap basemap. The realigned data has not been thoroughly checked for accuracy."
